  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to test whether the health care provider access and training in
      CERTAIN (Checklist for Early Recognition and Treatment of Acute Illness), would facilitate
      timely and error free best-practice delivery and minimize preventable death and costly
      complications in critically ill patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
